spec_data.Name: autogen-libopts
spec_data.Description:
Libopts is very powerful command line option parser consisting of a set of
AutoGen templates and a run time library that nearly eliminates the hassle of
parsing and documenting command line options.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 11:01:32 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Automated option processing library based on autogen
